item.title: Projects
item.description: PW-Card PW-Card is a webtool coded in python with the streamlit libary, to generate password cards. Did you know the problem when you forgot your password? With this tool, you don’t forget your password and if you loose the card, you can re-download your card with the restore feature! Interested? Look here HoloPlay-Desk HoloPlay-desk is a unofficial desktop client for HoloPlay with a private mode feature. Look here D-clean D-clean is a program to erase hard drives, secure!
